verbose_text: Expression of cell surface markers was determined by incubation of cells with mAb specific for CD45 (30-F11), CD4 (L3T4), CD8 (53-6.7), CD11b (M1/70), CD19 (1D3), CD25 (PC61), CD44 (IM7), CD62L (MEL-14), CD69 (H1.2F3), CD138 (281-2) (BD Bioscience, San Jose, CA), PD-1 (RMP1-30) (eBioScience) and F4/80 (CI : A3-1; Serotec, Raleigh, NC) for 30 min on ice.
